{"tid":1868090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"衛生防護中心：隔離營冇位 青衣確診者同住家屬留係屋企隔離","createTime":"2020-02-07T11:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T18:02:47.000Z","uid":177811,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a014e15e8908bb6f70256307117fe1e53e7a616","tid":1868090,"uid":177811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"突發消息 請大家小心<br />\n<br />\n確診患者家人並沒有送去隔離營，衛生防護中心終於打黎，解釋係隔離營爆滿 😡 民政事務署仲同我地講無需要通知區議員 <br />\n<br />\n真係講句，有無攪錯！你地唔同我地講，你地乜野都唔公佈，咁居民點？日日就係要等我地死追爛追先肯講！<br />\n<br />\n我而家要求緊衛生防護中心立即接走患者家人到隔離營！<br />\n<br />\n#好嬲<br />\n#大家小心<br />\n#你的安灝區議員 #WarrenTam #TeamWarren<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223290641506953/posts/809689486200396/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223290641506953%2Fposts%2F809689486200396%2F&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=c1a1dcc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223290641506953/posts/809689486200396/</a>"},{"pid":"d130cf2f5a317db704de4c568c70da96c2504dff","tid":1868090,"uid":177811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"冇位定留返d位接濟d大陸人？<br />\n冇位又唔公佈"},{"pid":"55866b966ea4b4fcdcefaceeb3ee3874890fbf90","tid":1868090,"uid":177811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4230f3c188cb7616be8853fb7433ae108ede46c3","tid":1868090,"uid":177811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5c376bd5cd9c25e4ee666ab27da6f125600f82","tid":1868090,"uid":177811,"l